data.description: home offers a large open kitchen with slab granite counter tops great for entertaining - its large family room - open to formal dining room, it's split plan. Master bedroom and bath are on the rear of the home. It has a great niche in the hallway for displaying your fine treasures or artwork. The additional bedrooms share a bath with a large double vanity and a linen closet. Also has a great yard and not too close to the neighbors. Many large windows to allow natural light. Sits on a premium Homesite. Beautiful dark wood floors and Ceramic tile in the living areas. High ceilings with can lights and ceiling fans.
